div.stage:
Enter Ate as before. Then let their follow Omphale daughter to the King of Lydia, having a club in her hand, and a lion's skin on her back, Hercules following with a distaff. Then let Omphale turn about, and taking off her pantofle, strike Hercules on the head, then let them depart. Ate remaining, saying;
Quem non argolici mandata severa tyranni,
Non potuit Juno vincere, vicit amor.
